history.content:
I am happy to announce that the Spring 2021 UC Berkeley Global Startup Fair, co-hosted by HKN, IEEE, and CSUA, will be taking place Tuesday, March 30 from 10:00 AM to 3:00 PM PDT.  Below you can find the registration link, the discord link where we can answer any questions you may have, and links to our social media.
  • Date: Tuesday 3/30
  • Time: 10am - 3pm PST
  • Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ucbstartupfair/
  • IG:  https://www.instagram.com/ucbglobalstartupfair/
  • Registration: https://ucbstartupfair.com/register
  • Discord: https://ucbstartupfair.com/discord
The UCB Global Startup Fair is a unique recruitment event where the spotlight is on the startups. It is a chance for small companies to speak directly to students without getting overshadowed by the big names.

We bring together the most innovative new companies around the world and introduce them to students from one of the top engineering universities in the world. When combined with the Startup Fair resume book, companies get access to hundreds of potential candidates who are looking for a job or internship with the opportunity for growth a startup provides.
